# ⚠️ HOW TO USE THIS LIST (IMPORTANT)

### Rule 1
Don’t skip. Difficulty compounds.

### Rule 2
Each project → GitHub commit.

### Rule 3
If stuck → break the project into **mini-features**.

### Rule 4
Finish ugly projects. Don’t restart.

